---

## Step 3 — Reference Parameter Ranges

If you need to tune a specific parameter beyond what the profile or recipe
specifies, consult `docs/params/` for valid ranges:

- `docs/params/physics.md` — L1: springs, easing, stagger
- `docs/params/visual.md` — L2: blur, scale, translate, opacity
- `docs/params/composition.md` — L3: typography, color, layout
- `docs/params/temporal.md` — L4: scene durations, BPM, beat grids
- `docs/params/techniques.md` — L5: reveal/transition/camera methods

Never guess parameter values when the docs have the answer.

---

## Step 4 — After Comparison

If a compare-ads result exists for this composition, read the latest
`compare-results/<compId>-iter<N>.json` and `docs/parameter-log.json`
to understand:

1. Which parameters were flagged as deltas
2. Whether previous adjustments improved the score
3. Which parameters still need work

Apply the `parameterDeltas` from the comparison result, prioritized
by confidence score.

---

## Quick reference — Spring presets

| Preset | stiffness | damping | mass | Profile |
|--------|-----------|---------|------|---------|
| SNAP | 200 | 25 | 0.8 | snappy-saas |
| PREMIUM_SPRING.hero | 90 | 22 | 1.1 | luxury-slow |
| SPRING.bouncy | 120 | 10 | 0.9 | kinetic-typography |
| PREMIUM_SPRING.text | 120 | 28 | 0.7 | all (text) |
| PREMIUM_SPRING.bg | 60 | 30 | 1.2 | luxury-slow (bg) |

## Quick reference — Minimum constraints

- spring.damping ≥ 18 for premium feel
- float.amplitude ≤ 8px
- float.periodFrames ≥ 70
- blur.textReveal ≤ 14px (>14 excessive)
- scene minimum 3s (90f at 30fps)
- CTA scene 2–3s
- depthDeemphasis opacity floor ≥ 0.35
